The players find themselves on the respective arenas.
Normal: Wacky Grasslands
Description: A simple and green grassland, full of wheat, trees, and a few houses. The statue has 250.000 Health in Normal.
_
Nightmare: Voluptous Show
Description: A large, wooden scenario. The whole map is a large scenario, with the statue being in the middle, and enemies spawning from left and right. The statue has 125.000 Health in Nightmare.
_
Epitome: Devastated Colliseum
Description: A large arena, albeit cut short. Enemies spawn from all directions. Good luck! The statue has 50.000 Health in Epitome.
